\q1 
\v 53 \w He|strong="G2532"\w* \w has|strong="G2532"\w* \w filled|strong="G1705"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w hungry|strong="G3983"\w* \w with|strong="G2532"\w* \w good|strong="G2532"\w* \w things|strong="G2756"\w*
\q2 \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w sent|strong="G1821"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w rich|strong="G4147"\w* \w away|strong="G1821"\w* \w empty|strong="G2756"\w*.\f + \fr 1:53 \ft This sounds like social justice.\f*
\q1 
\v 54 \w He|strong="G2474"\w* has taken \w the|strong="G3403"\w* part \w of|strong="G2474"\w* \w His|strong="G3403"\w* \w servant|strong="G3816"\w* \w Israel|strong="G2474"\w*,
\q2 in \w remembrance|strong="G3403"\w* \w of|strong="G2474"\w* \w mercy|strong="G1656"\w*,
\q1 
\v 55 \w just|strong="G2531"\w* \w as|strong="G2531"\w* \w He|strong="G2532"\w* \w spoke|strong="G2980"\w* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* \w our|strong="G2532"\w* \w fathers|strong="G3962"\w*,
\q2 \w to|strong="G1519"\w* Abraham \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* \w his|strong="G1519"\w* \w seed|strong="G4690"\w* \w while|strong="G2980"\w* \it there is\it* \w an|strong="G2532"\w* age.”\f + \fr 1:55 \ft I follow the best line of transmission, as I believe, albeit representing only 35% of the Greek manuscripts, in this case. I take the point to be that the things mentioned are pertinent to this world, not the next.\f*
\p 
\v 56 \w So|strong="G2532"\w* \w Mary|strong="G3137"\w* \w stayed|strong="G3306"\w* \w with|strong="G4862"\w* \w her|strong="G1519"\w* \w about|strong="G5613"\w* \w three|strong="G5140"\w* \w months|strong="G3376"\w*,\f + \fr 1:56 \ft Those three months in the home of a priest were doubtless filled with relevant instruction from the Scriptures (of course Zacharias was mute, so he would have to write everything), part of Mary's preparation for her role. Note that Mary evidently took off before John was born [I wonder why]. On the other hand, being three months pregnant it was high time that she go home and face the situation that awaited her. Although Joseph evidently took her to his house immediately, at God's direction, after only six months a full size baby would be born.\f* \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w returned|strong="G5290"\w* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* \w her|strong="G1519"\w* \w house|strong="G3624"\w*.
\ms1 The birth of John
