\v 27 “Further, \w to|strong="G3004"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w who|strong="G3588"\w* \w are|strong="G3588"\w* listening\f + \fr 6:27 \ft Are you ‘listening’? Really?\f* \w I|strong="G3004"\w* \w say|strong="G3004"\w*: Love \w your|strong="G4160"\w* \w enemies|strong="G2190"\w*, \w do|strong="G4160"\w* \w good|strong="G2573"\w* \w to|strong="G3004"\w* \w those|strong="G3588"\w* \w who|strong="G3588"\w* \w hate|strong="G3404"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w*;
