\s2 Two foundations
\p 
\v 46 “\w Why|strong="G5101"\w* \w do|strong="G4160"\w* \w you|strong="G3739"\w* \w call|strong="G2564"\w* \w me|strong="G1473"\w*, ‘\w Lord|strong="G2962"\w*, \w Lord|strong="G2962"\w*’, \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w not|strong="G3756"\w* \w do|strong="G4160"\w* \w what|strong="G5101"\w* \w I|strong="G1473"\w* \w say|strong="G3004"\w*?\f + \fr 6:46 \ft This is presumably one of the questions that will be on the Final Test.\f*
