\s1 Light inside the body
\p 
\v 33 “\w No|strong="G3762"\w* \w one|strong="G3762"\w*, having lit \w a|strong="G1519"\w* \w lamp|strong="G3088"\w*, \w puts|strong="G5087"\w* \w it|strong="G5087"\w* \w in|strong="G1519"\w* hiding \w or|strong="G3761"\w* \w under|strong="G5259"\w* \w a|strong="G1519"\w* \w basket|strong="G3426"\w*, \w but|strong="G3762"\w* \w on|strong="G1909"\w* \w its|strong="G5259"\w* stand, \w so|strong="G2443"\w* \w that|strong="G2443"\w* \w those|strong="G3588"\w* \w who|strong="G3588"\w* \w come|strong="G1531"\w* \w in|strong="G1519"\w* \w may|strong="G2443"\w* see \w the|strong="G1519"\w* \w light|strong="G5338"\w*.
\v 34 \w The|strong="G2532"\w* \w lamp|strong="G3088"\w* \w of|strong="G2532"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w body|strong="G4983"\w* \w is|strong="G1510"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w eye|strong="G3788"\w*.\f + \fr 11:34 \ft Of course we have two eyes, but the Text has “eye” in the singular. I take it that the reference is to the way we interpret what we see (which is our real ‘eye’)—two people, one pure and one vile, observing the same scene will give very different interpretations to it. ‘Malignant’ means aggressively evil. Someone with a malignant mind will give an evil interpretation to \nd everything\nd* he sees, and in consequence his being will be filled with unrelenting darkness. See Titus 1:15.\f* \w Therefore|strong="G1161"\w*, \w whenever|strong="G3752"\w* \w your|strong="G3650"\w* ‘\w eye|strong="G3788"\w*’ \w is|strong="G1510"\w* \w good|strong="G3588"\w*, \w your|strong="G3650"\w* \w whole|strong="G3650"\w* \w body|strong="G4983"\w* \w is|strong="G1510"\w* illuminated. \w But|strong="G1161"\w* \w when|strong="G3752"\w* \w it|strong="G2532"\w* \w is|strong="G1510"\w* \w malignant|strong="G4190"\w*, \w your|strong="G3650"\w* \w body|strong="G4983"\w* \w also|strong="G2532"\w* \w is|strong="G1510"\w* darkened.
\v 35 \w So|strong="G3767"\w* \w see|strong="G4648"\w* \w to|strong="G1722"\w* \w it|strong="G1510"\w* \w that|strong="G3588"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* ‘\w light|strong="G5457"\w*’ \w in|strong="G1722"\w* \w you|strong="G4771"\w* \w not|strong="G3361"\w* \w be|strong="G1510"\w* \w darkness|strong="G4655"\w*.
\v 36 \w If|strong="G1487"\w* \w then|strong="G3767"\w* \w your|strong="G3650"\w* \w whole|strong="G3650"\w* \w body|strong="G4983"\w* \w is|strong="G1510"\w* \w full|strong="G5460"\w* \w of|strong="G4983"\w* \w light|strong="G5461"\w*, \w not|strong="G3361"\w* \w having|strong="G2192"\w* \w any|strong="G5100"\w* \w part|strong="G3313"\w* \w dark|strong="G4652"\w*, \w the|strong="G3588"\w* \w whole|strong="G3650"\w* \w will|strong="G1510"\w* \w be|strong="G1510"\w* \w illuminated|strong="G5461"\w*, \w as|strong="G5613"\w* \w when|strong="G3752"\w* \w the|strong="G3588"\w* \w bright|strong="G5460"\w* shining \w of|strong="G4983"\w* \w a|strong="G2192"\w* \w lamp|strong="G3088"\w* gives \w you|strong="G4771"\w* \w light|strong="G5461"\w*.”
\s1 Jesus derides scribes and Pharisees
\p 
\v 37 \w Now|strong="G1161"\w* \w as|strong="G1722"\w* \w He|strong="G1161"\w* \w spoke|strong="G2980"\w*, \w a|strong="G1722"\w* certain \w Pharisee|strong="G5330"\w* \w invited|strong="G2065"\w* \w Him|strong="G3588"\w* \w to|strong="G1722"\w* eat \w with|strong="G1722"\w* \w him|strong="G3588"\w*. \w So|strong="G1161"\w* \w He|strong="G1161"\w* \w went|strong="G1525"\w* \w in|strong="G1722"\w* \w and|strong="G1161"\w* reclined.
\v 38 \w But|strong="G1161"\w* \w the|strong="G1161"\w* \w Pharisee|strong="G5330"\w*, noticing \w that|strong="G3754"\w* \w He|strong="G1161"\w* \w did|strong="G3708"\w* \w not|strong="G3756"\w* \w first|strong="G4413"\w* wash \w before|strong="G4253"\w* \w the|strong="G1161"\w* meal, \w was|strong="G3588"\w* critical.\f + \fr 11:38 \ft The leaders had already rejected Jesus and were planning to kill Him, so He knew this was not a friendly invitation. He accepted the invitation with the clear purpose to provoke a confrontation.\f*
\v 39 \w So|strong="G2532"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w Lord|strong="G2962"\w* \w said|strong="G3004"\w* \w to|strong="G4314"\w* \w him|strong="G3588"\w*: “\w Now|strong="G1161"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w Pharisees|strong="G5330"\w* \w clean|strong="G2511"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w outside|strong="G1855"\w* \w of|strong="G2532"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w cup|strong="G4221"\w* \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* dish, \w but|strong="G1161"\w* \w your|strong="G2962"\w* \w inside|strong="G2081"\w* \w is|strong="G3588"\w* \w full|strong="G1073"\w* \w of|strong="G2532"\w* greed \w and|strong="G2532"\w* malignancy.
