\s1 Jesus dismisses His spirit
\p 
\v 44 \w Now|strong="G2532"\w* \w it|strong="G2532"\w* \w was|strong="G1510"\w* \w about|strong="G5616"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w sixth|strong="G1623"\w* \w hour|strong="G5610"\w*,\f + \fr 23:44 \ft Luke uses Jewish time, so it was about noon.\f* \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w darkness|strong="G4655"\w* \w came|strong="G1096"\w* \w upon|strong="G1909"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w whole|strong="G3650"\w* \w land|strong="G1093"\w* \w until|strong="G2193"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w ninth|strong="G1766"\w* \w hour|strong="G5610"\w*.
